{
  "_comment": [
    "Benchmark sweep configuration for the ExaMPM Material Point Method proxy app.",
    "Each scenario maps to one BenchmarkScenario object in metrics_collector.py.",
    "",
    "Application: ExaMPM (ECP proxy for material point method codes)",
    "Executable:  DamBreak",
    "CLI argument format:",
    "  <cell_size> <parts_per_cell> <halo_cells> <dt> <t_end> <write_freq> <exec_space>",
    "",
    "Example: ./DamBreak 0.05 2 0 0.001 1.0 10 serial",
    "",
    "Design:",
    "  - Fixed 2 MPI processes for all scenarios (ExaMPM partitions in Y only).",
    "  - 3 workload sizes controlled by t_end (simulation end time):",
    "      short  : t_end = 0.05  (50 timesteps at dt=0.001)",
    "      medium : t_end = 0.10  (100 timesteps at dt=0.001)",
    "      long   : t_end = 0.20  (200 timesteps at dt=0.001)",
    "  - Cell size 0.1 keeps the problem small enough for fast validation.",
    "  - For each workload: 1 failure-free baseline + 5 failure scenarios",
    "    with injection delays of 5s, 10s, 20s, 40s, and 80s.",
    "  - Total: 3 × (1 + 5) = 18 scenarios."
  ],
